FAQ

What is Wix?

Wix is a global SaaS website builder platform with 280M+ users worldwide. Wix empowers users to create, manage and grow a business presence online.

What is a Wix channel partnership?

Wix Channels empowers industry-leading enterprises to provide Wix’s web creation platform and business solutions directly to small business customers.

What are the benefits of being a Wix channel partner?

Wix channel partners benefit from increased revenue, customer retention and acquisition. By adding Wix to their services, channel partners gain an edge in their industry, providing small business customers with a comprehensive solution.


Wix channel partners are able to seamlessly offer their customers the best web creation platform out there for small businesses, while receiving tailored service and support from a complete B2B ecosystem.


  • Maximize your offering to small business customers, providing them with everything they need throughout the business lifecycle.

  • Partner with a powerful brand that has led the way in small business online presence and innovation for nearly 20 years.

  • Enjoy the B2B infrastructure that enables top-notch technical integrations, flexible GTM models and dedicated support, all tailored to the needs of your company.

What channel partnership models do you offer at Wix?

At Wix, we believe in tailored partnerships. We have the ability to customize the partnership according to your industry and company needs to help ensure success. Our channel partnerships may also include bi-lateral aspects for synergy and maximum impact.

We’ll work together to determine which Wix solutions you offer to your customer base, the user journey to the offering, your website service fulfillment type (DIY, DIWM, DIFM), billing ownership and more.

What is the difference between being a Wix channel partner and a Wix affiliate?

A Wix channel partner (or Wix reseller) is an enterprise that engages in a high-touch, strategic B2B partnership to offer Wix services directly to their small business customers.

A Wix affiliate is a website owner that promotes Wix through original content as part of a marketing arrangement.

Is the Wix reseller solution a white label solution?

While not a white label solution, Wix gives its channel partners the opportunity to leverage the power of the Wix brand by co-branding services and providing them as part of the channel partner’s offering.

What kind of enterprise businesses can resell Wix services?

Wix partners with leading enterprises across markets and industries that serve small business customers—including SaaS, creator services, directories, banks and fintech and more.
